<div class="main-content">
    <hgroup>
        <h1>Basic Swap</h1>
        <p>The simplest HTMX + Swap.Htmx interaction</p>
    </hgroup>
    
    <h2>Live Demo</h2>
    <div class="demo-area">
        <div id="message-container">
            <p>Click the button to load a message from the server.</p>
            <button hx-get="/Patterns/GetMessage" 
                    hx-target="#message-container" 
                    hx-swap="innerHTML">
                Load Message
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Button has <code>hx-get="/Patterns/GetMessage"</code> to make a GET request</li>
        <li>Response targets <code>#message-container</code></li>
        <li>Server returns a partial view using <code>Swap().Target().Partial()</code></li>
    </ol>
    
    <h2>Controller Code</h2>
    <div class="code-view">
<pre>[HttpGet]
public IActionResult GetMessage()
{
    return Swap()
        .Target("#message-container")
        .Partial("_Message", new { 
            Message = $"Hello! The time is {DateTime.Now:HH:mm:ss}" 
        });
}</pre>
    </div>
    
    <h2>View Code</h2>
    <div class="code-view">
<pre>&lt;div id="message-container"&gt;
    &lt;button hx-get="/Patterns/GetMessage" 
            hx-target="#message-container" 
            hx-swap="innerHTML"&gt;
        Load Message
    &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
    </div>
    
    <h2>Partial View (_Message.cshtml)</h2>
    <div class="code-view">
<pre>@@model dynamic
&lt;p&gt;@@Model.Message&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;button hx-get="/Patterns/GetMessage" 
        hx-target="#message-container" 
        hx-swap="innerHTML"&gt;
    Refresh
&lt;/button&gt;</pre>
    </div>
    
    <h2>Key Points</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><code>Swap()</code> is available on <code>SwapController</code> base class</li>
        <li><code>.Target()</code> sets the CSS selector for the swap</li>
        <li><code>.Partial()</code> renders a Razor partial view</li>
        <li>The response replaces only the targeted element</li>
    </ul>
</div>
